text: Dasmosmilia is a genus of small corals in the family Caryophylliidae. ==Species== The World Register of Marine Species includes the following species in the genus: * Dasmosmilia lymani (Pourtalès, 1871) * Dasmosmilia variegata (Pourtalès, 1871) ==References== Category:Caryophylliidae Category:Scleractinia genera
title: Dasmosmilia
